{"tid":1579860,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"出街食飯找錢有毫子會點處理?","createTime":"2019-09-18T19:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T12:21:05.000Z","uid":75868,"like":34,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"69c4d75d2662e4127188728c1f61d10bf1bebdaf","tid":1579860,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:04:34.000Z","msg":"雖然應該唔會有餐牌個價錢係有毫子<br />\n但計埋加一又唔四捨五入就有機會找到毫子比你<br />\n而家找錢又唔會直接交落你雙手，櫃檯埋單就擺落個盤，行埋你檯埋單就擺係個皮夾入面<br />\n毫子拎完基本上唔會再有機會用到，買野九成地方又唔收<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老虎蟹都拎哂佢<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毫子要黎做乜，擺低佢留係到"},{"pid":"57e9270f00a4d98258fb3d8fe4ec94e3b92f0a5c","tid":1579860,"uid":229369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:08:20.000Z","msg":"拎撚晒啦<br />\n<br />\n搭車用<br />\n買嘢用<br />\n下次食飯用<br />\n<br />\n宜家大把嘢仲係有毫子位啦"},{"pid":"e331183d6b6663acecaded3c4a263cb4e070c3a7","tid":1579860,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:09:19.000Z","msg":"一野彈番落個收銀度"},{"pid":"9f3bc9249983bed57b5513705aee806deb4a2e35","tid":1579860,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e9270f00a4d98258fb3d8fe4ec94e3b92f0a5c","tid":1579860,"uid":229369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:08:20.000Z","msg":"拎撚晒啦<br />\n<br />\n搭車用<br />\n買嘢用<br />\n下次食飯用<br />\n<br />\n宜家大把嘢仲係有毫子位啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:10:22.000Z","msg":"銀包有毫子而下次要用毫子就即用<br />\n唔好儲埋一齊然後唔知點用<br />\n我銀仔都係咁處理"},{"pid":"2227f88d1feeb5029bb6e80adf2c7849d280c734","tid":1579860,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:10:56.000Z","msg":"有散銀車收毫子架，Check吓幾時到你嗰一區啦"},{"pid":"54a879dcea4152f2bb1f466c874963a47d6a7238","tid":1579860,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e331183d6b6663acecaded3c4a263cb4e070c3a7","tid":1579860,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:09:19.000Z","msg":"一野彈番落個收銀度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:11:16.000Z","msg":"儲起攞嚟扔Popo"},{"pid":"2e4eb23f69653dd6c1f5b6fecf7adbea4e4f0a74","tid":1579860,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"儲埋佢等收銀車<br />\n舊年拓住成罐去比收銀車<br />\n數完原來有成差不多三舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全數入晒落八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b08668190f14ec87aed54e28ef84fb4832d5a58","tid":1579860,"uid":320778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:15:57.000Z","msg":"通常會諗辦法洗咗佢<br />\n例如有4毫子係身<br />\n經過7仔視乎情況可能會買少少嘢食或者嘢飲<br />\n夾埋條數一定要係xx個4先會行去俾錢<br />\n又或者搭車會用得着4毫子<br />\n我寧願用散紙都唔用八達通俾<br />\n如果真係洗唔曬先攞返屋企攞個罐裝住"},{"pid":"db5e4d7c3d76f65802f5d29d51f81b8330fc1a57","tid":1579860,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T21:19:10.000Z","msg":"用換幣龍或者Heycoin啲機入落銀行、八達通或者Tap$Go<br />\n上星期入咗八九十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVrmr9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVrmr9e.png&h=99f0b83d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5b6fc7ad0c65b0d6fbab208fd9d1aa52e5ef963","tid":1579860,"uid":104669,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:40:02.000Z","msg":"以前唔止毫子唔拎<br />\n連其他散子都唔拎當俾tips<br />\n而家罷用八達通<br />\n老閪都拎返 用嚟搭巴士用"},{"pid":"3c7275d42d78b7a7d6c100ed1d0bab2596f4e7db","tid":1579860,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db5e4d7c3d76f65802f5d29d51f81b8330fc1a57","tid":1579860,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T21:19:10.000Z","msg":"用換幣龍或者Heycoin啲機入落銀行、八達通或者Tap$Go<br />\n上星期入咗八九十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVrmr9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVrmr9